energy.usef.core.data.xml.bean.message

Class SettlementMessageResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • energy.usef.core.data.xml.bean.message.SettlementMessageResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message

    public class SettlementMessageResponse
extends Object
implements Message
    Upon receiving and processing a SettlementMessage, the receiving implementation must reply with a SettlementMessageResponse, indicating whether the initial message was handled successfully. In case a SettlementMessage is rejected, the sender of the original message should consider all FlexOrderSettlement elements in that message to be disputed.

    Java class for SettlementMessageResponse element declaration.
